e was materially misleading at the time it induced Peter's reliance.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_083fdb9afb5842beb4a4e49b","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"The admitted record shows Samantha's authenticated confession (PX-4) that she had not read Stephenson before drafting and implied she had, while simultaneously assuring Peter the package would be complete by the March 11 hand"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"The admitted record shows Samantha's authenticated confession (PX-4) that she had not read Stephenson before drafting and implied she had, while simultaneously assuring Peter the package would be complete by the March 11 hand","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-02-15","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782756726877,"responseId":"gen-1782756727-9MhNrvS4NrtfYdIc6CZ7","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3.5-plus-20260216"}}
